Class PSProperty

java.lang.Object
  ipworksssh.PSProperty

public class PSProperty
extends java.lang.Object

A property in a PowerShell object

This type describes a specific property of a PowerShell object returned after pipeline execution.

A property has a name, a data type, a value and a boolean property indicating if it's null.

DataType: The type of this property

Each property has a unique name, a value, a type and a boolean value indicating if it's null.

IsNull: True, if the property has a null value

Each property has a unique name, a value, a type and a boolean value indicating if it's null.

Name: The name of a property

Each property has a unique name, a value, a type and a boolean value indicating if it's null.

Value: The value of this property

Each property has a unique name, a value, a type and a boolean value indicating if it's null.

Certmgr, Certmgr.PSProperty
